{"tid":2179194,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人同我一樣睇鄭鋪滿(志兄)最新嗰條精神病訪問睇到咸撚咗？","createTime":"2020-08-29T02:46:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-29T09:16:13.000Z","uid":73381,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f87b46dc3f80f49d6496a578886fb94bd91ee670","tid":2179194,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T02:46:16.000Z","msg":"勁撚勵志(理志(禮志)) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/104910377711056/posts/189668212568605/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F104910377711056%2Fposts%2F189668212568605%2F&d=aJB%2Bq6ruafnyRbkwc%2FW5Zs4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=08dbb85c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/104910377711056/posts/189668212568605/</a>"},{"pid":"0664bb48d582750b3ea5246eba9d1a9211ee01d5","tid":2179194,"uid":171273,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T02:47:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"02361acfccf1df8ae5a38c243ee22b79711b685a","tid":2179194,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T02:47:37.000Z","msg":"【#我與精神健康的距離－鄭錦滿（1）】更需要真誠聽取患者心聲<br />\n<br />\n做運動本身對身心健康有益。<br />\n但在這場疫症下，很多公共空間關閉。<br />\n可能您說可以在家做運動，但奈何不是所有人有足夠空間。<br />\n物質未必最重要，更重要的是身邊人的真誠關懷。<br />\n<br />\n精神健康不是一個人的事，需要社會各界關注，與您同行。<br />\n今日我們請來熱血公民成員 鄭錦滿 講解他對精神健康的理解，讓彼此距離拉近。"},{"pid":"a2467e1e727a346a22013b50800443c7f37d60cc","tid":2179194,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0664bb48d582750b3ea5246eba9d1a9211ee01d5","tid":2179194,"uid":171273,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T02:47:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T02:47:59.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"727c938b02f1e73d5644b75ff99e6405723ad7f5","tid":2179194,"uid":283207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"p